PURPOSE:

This is a kind of chat room program in which we will be creating a server with the port number given from the server . The user can also be logged in as the client and there can be multiple clients . the clients can input various values to the server and the server will check whether the given number is prime or not . If the given number is prime it server will store the client name and the prime number in the data structure .

I have used the hashMap as the datastructure to store the data of the user.



PERCENT COMPLETE:

 "I believe I have completed 100% of this project."


