BUGS:

N/A


FILES:

Included with this project are 16 files:

README, the text file you are present viewing
build.xml, the ant file required for building ,cleaning and runing
PrimeDriver.java , contains the main driver to start the client driver and server driver according to the user input
ClientDriver.java , Contains the driver to drive the client according to user input
ClientMenu.java , Contains the menu for the client to use
ClientInterface.java , contains the menu which the ClientDriver has
ServerInterface.java , contains the methods implemented by the ServerDriver
ServerDriver.java , main method which contains driver code for Server 
AllPrimeQueries.java , contains the datastructure and it's related operations for client data
ServerMenu.java , contains the menu to display the server menu
PrimeServerSocket.java , contains the code for creaton of server socket  
PrimeServerWorker.java , contains the code to create threads to accept several connections from clients
PrimeClientSocket.java , contains the code to create the sockets of the client .
PrimeClientWorker.java , contains the code to send and recieve messages from the server
CheckPrime.java , contains the code to check whether the number input from client is prime or not 
Debug.java , contains the code to display the messages to the user at various debug levels

